info.title: KanTime EVV Open API
info.description:
# Overview
**Open API for integrating third party systems with the KanTime**

This is a data exchange API used for KanTime Visit Adjudication. It is used to render information regarding authorizations and schedule details for Clients and also helps to reduce fradulent data and enhance compliance.

The API has the main entities of Caregivers, Rates, Authorizations and Visits.
- **Caregivers** (sometimes called Attendants) is the individual who performs the service.
- **Rates** defines the values used to payroll the visits.
- **Authorization** defines the eligibilty of Clients undertaing the care services.
- **Visits** are appointments planned for Clients to provide care.

# Authentication 
Third party system shall send **agency specific API key** in `X-CC-API-Key` HTTP header field.
